dct_title_s: Insurance maps, Paterson, New Jersey : volume one
dct_description_sm: Includes key, key map, map of congested district, streets and specials index, and text. "297." "General index to Sanborn maps of Paterson, N.J., vols. I, II, & III" on preliminary sheets [1-3]. "Map of congested district of Paterson, N.J., 1915" (scale 200 ft. to an inch) on preliminary sheet [6].
